# Card-art masters live here, one per card: assets/cards-src/<key>.png
# (1024×1434, 5:7 portrait, PNG). The filename is the card's stable catalog
# `key`. Drop a master here and run `make cards-images` to deliver it; cards
# without a master fall back to the shared placeholder. Generated by the
# external AI image tool via tools/gen_card_art.py. See docs/decisions/card_images.md.
#
# This file just keeps the directory in git; real masters are committed alongside it.
